# Playwright Java Maven Framework

This repository contains a **Playwright test automation framework built with Java and Maven**, designed with scalability, maintainability, and CI/CD integration in mind.

It is suitable for UI test automation and can be easily extended with additional features such as Page Object Model, parallel execution, reporting, and environment configuration.

