ğŸ§ª Test Design
PlaywrightFactory
Centralized browser lifecycle management

BaseTest
Handles setup and teardown for each test

Tests extend BaseTest for clean test isolation

ğŸ”„ Continuous Integration (CI)
This project includes GitHub Actions CI.

The pipeline:

Triggers on push and pull_request

Sets up Java 17

Installs Playwright browsers

Runs all tests headlessly

